                        <description>&lt;p&gt;We have customers reporting errors such as:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Caused by: java.lang.NullPointerException&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.lucene.store.FSDirectory.create(FSDirectory.java:200)&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.lucene.store.FSDirectory.getDirectory(FSDirectory.java:144)&lt;br/&gt;
